data.description: Best Property in Hesperia. Exciting opportunity in Hesperia! Prepare to be amazed by this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home with a stunning open floor plan plan with 1346 square feet of living space. The open floor plan seamlessly integrates an amazing kitchen, designed to cater to your every need. Whether you're entertaining guests or simply preparing your daily meals, this kitchen is up to the task. Equipped with appliances and offering generous storage and counter space. The property sits on an outstanding lot, boasting over 1/2 acre of prime real estate. Talk about a business gem! With Complementary breathtaking mountain views. Call me today
